column5: ....Well I guess it always possible to set new bench marks and apparently I've just found mine. Have a look at this incredible custom rod work.      A number of amazing custom rod photos can be seen here....  http://www.fieldandstream.com/article_gallery.jsp?ID=1000021904
....I wish I could take the credit Glen as it is amazing work but alas no, it was not I.
Neat.  Knew some guys on here make their own rods, this post might spur a new entrepreneurial endeavor.  Very cool graphics.
that is a thing of beauty
It is an excellent display of craftsmanship!
That is in freaking credible. Nice find.
